comments: Lee (PHX) extends his forearm against Plumlee's (LAC) side, which affects Plumlee's SQBR as he dribbles toward the lane.
Okogie (PHX) and Westbrook (LAC) mutually engage and disengage as the pick is set.
Lee (PHX) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
After initially getting his hand on the ball, Batum's (LAC) hand slides off Bazley (PHX), and marginal contact occurs.
Bazley (PHX) shuffles his feet after his gather.
Batum (LAC) is drawn into the air and initiates contact with Bazley's (PHX) arm and body, which affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Lee (PHX) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) legally contests Bazley's (PHX) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Lee (PHX) moves alongside Westbrook's (LAC) path and absorbs the contact during Westbrook's drive toward the rim.
Westbrook (LAC) reaches for the ensuing pass and makes contact with the ball before following through and causing marginal contact to occur with Bazley (PHX) in the lane.
Westbrook (LAC) firms up in Okogie's (PHX) path, and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Lee (PHX) retracts his resting hand from Leonard (LAC) as Leonard enters his shooting motion, and the contact is marginal.
Westbrook (LAC) comes across Lee's (PHX) arm as he contests the shot attempt, and the contact affects Lee's ability to finish.
Leonard (LAC) is retreating in Okogie's (PHX) path before legally contesting the shot attempt.
